nths) as alternatives for high-deduction or post-record-year scenarios. SBA 7(a) coordination for brokerage acquisition financing. Real estate is non-SSTB under Section 199A favorable QBI treatment regardless of income level." canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/real-estate-agent/">
  <div class="realtor-scope" set:html={realtorBody} />
</Layout>

<style is:global>
.realtor-scope{
